==Indonesian==
===Verb===
'''tinggal'''

# to [[live]]
# to [[stay]]

====Usage====
* "[[selamat tinngal|Selamat tinggal]]" means "[[goodbye]]", but is only said to a person who is staying where they are. 

===Derived terms===
* [[meninggal]] ''to [[die]]''
* [[meninggalkan]] ''to [[leave]] (something/someone)''

